    chapterContext: "In chapter 5, Paul discusses the hope of eternal life and our heavenly dwelling. He explains that believers live by faith, not by sight, and that our goal is to please God. Paul then reveals the ministry of reconciliation—that God was reconciling the world to Himself through Christ.",
